00/fcc92b344c370e23d77749d2e9be2801ff04349c.png 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cb936190940b21f3cf4b1c291f5e6f67/5b89e6de49b99248-0a/s250x400/b65331d80a93c53cff604455f70851e20ebb07d0.png 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cb936190940b21f3cf4b1c291f5e6f67/5b89e6de49b99248-0a/s400x600/c52c7a385e0e9ed722708569d62925f205fec7e7.png 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cb936190940b21f3cf4b1c291f5e6f67/5b89e6de49b99248-0a/s500x750/e1d3954aac7e1a69a39a9597cb7f096024a557c8.png 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cb936190940b21f3cf4b1c291f5e6f67/5b89e6de49b99248-0a/s540x810/4e641ae920abcf1aed677e6d2b3c0beea98030df.png 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cb936190940b21f3cf4b1c291f5e6f67/5b89e6de49b99248-0a/s640x960/a3a63222eab4830c806be6c46ceb35d1be6ec5e8.png 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cb936190940b21f3cf4b1c291f5e6f67/5b89e6de49b99248-0a/s1280x1920/031e36515fa0933432477939ca8d2f7403f5b338.png 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cb936190940b21f3cf4b1c291f5e6f67/5b89e6de49b99248-0a/s2048x3072/63c800cee380789533eba411fe6f1cc683fdf010.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px"/&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Traveling within a city usually tends to become a hassle specially if it&amp;rsquo;s far distance, you&amp;rsquo;re an outsider and you&amp;rsquo;re on a budget. Commuting in the capital was largely a delight thanks to the lovely colorful strands of noodles spread all over and even outside the city. Although the Pink line was close to my heart for more than one reason, I enjoyed the punctual Yellow line too. The older Blue, Red and Yellow routes run &lt;a href="https://href.li/?https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bombardier_Movia" target="_blank"&gt;Bombardier&lt;/a&gt; rolling stock which have a very soothing warm lighting. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="npf_row"&gt;&lt;figure class="tmblr-full" data-orig-height="2380" data-orig-width="3197"&gt;&lt;img src="https://64.media.tumblr.com/7cb28f616512ff72821aca6380948258/5b89e6de49b99248-9a/s640x960/ce33954f489fe2e6ac554e3cd7d5af60d3e8e576.jpg" data-orig-height="2380" data-orig-width="3197" srcset="https://64.media.tumblr.com/7cb28f616512ff72821aca6380948258/5b89e6de49b99248-9a/s75x75_c1/d76b9273cee014ba3a848e1e57ced935229411ce.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7cb28f616512ff72821aca6380948258/5b89e6de49b99248-9a/s100x200/4706c535b8ed7ab027b813fe9e62623ca732f7dc.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7cb28f616512ff72821aca6380948258/5b89e6de49b99248-9a/s250x400/aaef3d2668d21c6dbce21e0c85c80b6dfce2ce6b.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7cb28f616512ff72821aca6380948258/5b89e6de49b99248-9a/s400x600/a027d2237dadb5707d8f8bd03e42c9214d19d007.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7cb28f616512ff72821aca6380948258/5b89e6de49b99248-9a/s500x750/eb2dae9dc1a6f6f6944632add44dd108dff6d0db.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7cb28f616512ff72821aca6380948258/5b89e6de49b99248-9a/s540x810/48080e68a2e247310c473c93cb3d3ebd3b64221a.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7cb28f616512ff72821aca6380948258/5b89e6de49b99248-9a/s640x960/ce33954f489fe2e6ac554e3cd7d5af60d3e8e576.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7cb28f616512ff72821aca6380948258/5b89e6de49b99248-9a/s1280x1920/f3a135eb4bc59185af9523ef72269e52f2c2a254.jpg 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7cb28f616512ff72821aca6380948258/5b89e6de49b99248-9a/s2048x3072/e4789c0e16231eac4ccc5928f81ca56a465aef2b.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px"/&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;What&amp;rsquo;s more soothing were the dot matrix displays running serif typography. There was something deeply satisfying in watching the beautifully crafted letterforms glide across the displays specially when in comparison to the LCD panels in the more modern &lt;a href="https://href.li/?https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hyundai_Rotem" target="_blank"&gt;Hyundai Rotem&lt;/a&gt; rolling stock. Granted the LCD displays are much more functional, in displaying various kinds of information at the same time, being easy to customize and monetized but there is something about the carefully arranged dots in the serif display that just feels welcoming, warm and human. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="npf_row"&gt;&lt;figure class="tmblr-full" data-orig-height="3120" data-orig-width="4160"&gt;&lt;img src="https://64.media.tumblr.com/d9bcdea7dfaf0a4ac5cdc265a0c3e5d7/5b89e6de49b99248-f9/s640x960/3ebdf36c8ada943f0c783e0d003766568800ee8c.jpg" data-orig-height="3120" data-orig-width="4160" srcset="https://64.media.tumblr.com/d9bcdea7dfaf0a4ac5cdc265a0c3e5d7/5b89e6de49b99248-f9/s75x75_c1/cb6390a5a3bb773e39c3ed4428d31ed4323d16c1.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d9bcdea7dfaf0a4ac5cdc265a0c3e5d7/5b89e6de49b99248-f9/s100x200/c03392a8c9ce93c47ef6b7d279d87cbb1cbfc286.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d9bcdea7dfaf0a4ac5cdc265a0c3e5d7/5b89e6de49b99248-f9/s250x400/89fc75712c4665a253d567fe00b4c7895b2447a4.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d9bcdea7dfaf0a4ac5cdc265a0c3e5d7/5b89e6de49b99248-f9/s400x600/049b0ee90d9386d9b2e385382c9cc74e12fac791.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d9bcdea7dfaf0a4ac5cdc265a0c3e5d7/5b89e6de49b99248-f9/s500x750/dc5270fa315af6198346daa719f6015db59793dd.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d9bcdea7dfaf0a4ac5cdc265a0c3e5d7/5b89e6de49b99248-f9/s540x810/82eb5cd6c5ca1e9c5810fcb2d6d4f8f7f11e5647.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d9bcdea7dfaf0a4ac5cdc265a0c3e5d7/5b89e6de49b99248-f9/s640x960/3ebdf36c8ada943f0c783e0d003766568800ee8c.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d9bcdea7dfaf0a4ac5cdc265a0c3e5d7/5b89e6de49b99248-f9/s1280x1920/d8fb2bc8eeffb1b2659fb74519a0c0b7f122daac.jpg 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d9bcdea7dfaf0a4ac5cdc265a0c3e5d7/5b89e6de49b99248-f9/s2048x3072/9fb083e88ccc0f045c65508cc062ac8616caa14e.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px"/&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;The soft curves of the serif work better with the Devanagari script and the use of color seems far more deliberate. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="npf_row"&gt;&lt;figure class="tmblr-full" data-orig-height="657" data-orig-width