other hand, reminded me of looney tunes, same reason you&amp;rsquo;ll see them here.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="npf_row"&gt;&lt;figure class="tmblr-full" data-orig-height="1200" data-orig-width="1200"&gt;&lt;img src="https://64.media.tumblr.com/2a122edb5b69c65e7d88367e8234b3b9/ed3cc45e293f79b1-6d/s640x960/dbdd61cda171d36a4928410b8b5b1955acc6a5f7.png" data-orig-height="1200" data-orig-width="1200" srcset="https://64.media.tumblr.com/2a122edb5b69c65e7d88367e8234b3b9/ed3cc45e293f79b1-6d/s75x75_c1/b20b78d2d7046fbf45e8f23987943435946cc7c2.png 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/2a122edb5b69c65e7d88367e8234b3b9/ed3cc45e293f79b1-6d/s100x200/857c7c8c9a30eba5850d44261dd4a5e4aec76f95.png 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/2a122edb5b69c65e7d88367e8234b3b9/ed3cc45e293f79b1-6d/s250x400/5c3a4ca227f8842b25150840f9fce9ecef212992.png 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/2a122edb5b69c65e7d88367e8234b3b9/ed3cc45e293f79b1-6d/s400x600/d69a99c9948a1fede8ba066581d5f73e1116bcbb.png 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/2a122edb5b69c65e7d88367e8234b3b9/ed3cc45e293f79b1-6d/s500x750/7fd106b78f3b1a5821c99886b3536b08c854b363.png 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/2a122edb5b69c65e7d88367e8234b3b9/ed3cc45e293f79b1-6d/s540x810/8a2d28c4897763fca7d74f239ff4b8d3e62ba807.png 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/2a122edb5b69c65e7d88367e8234b3b9/ed3cc45e293f79b1-6d/s640x960/dbdd61cda171d36a4928410b8b5b1955acc6a5f7.png 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/2a122edb5b69c65e7d88367e8234b3b9/ed3cc45e293f79b1-6d/s1280x1920/f333118f6a6e268ad4daf05fe7fd02eeee7f8dd1.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"/&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;This guy had football studs on while his friends were running around in sandals and slippers. Needless to say, he dribbled a lot, passed less and kept yelling at his team mates. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="npf_row"&gt;&lt;figure class="tmblr-full" data-orig-height="1200" data-orig-width="1200"&gt;&lt;img src="https://64.media.tumblr.com/8d43cf841dab6f79c26db40e0e368632/ed3cc45e293f7