miting news/ episodes/ music, a neck affixed at an angle fixated on the old loyal thumb not weary yet, having swiped away kilometers already. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="npf_row"&gt;&lt;figure class="tmblr-full" data-orig-height="1200" data-orig-width="2484"&gt;&lt;img src="https://64.media.tumblr.com/0a913d03df90380cb52ea6ebe1a5745d/662d3554b26c1b80-1e/s640x960/0f503a083fa67b9df5548349ab62704e74e44564.jpg" data-orig-height="1200" data-orig-width="2484" srcset="https://64.media.tumblr.com/0a913d03df90380cb52ea6ebe1a5745d/662d3554b26c1b80-1e/s75x75_c1/60a6b5e0b9530d2fb8bb253f5a58c910a8d3f01b.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/0a913d03df90380cb52ea6ebe1a5745d/662d3554b26c1b80-1e/s100x200/1457295ba22dc252df61a1048c5caaada7aaec2c.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/0a913d03df90380cb52ea6ebe1a5745d/662d3554b26c1b80-1e/s250x400/247b6aa4c8ddacd07deaf52ae285039288e42722.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/0a913d03df90380cb52ea6ebe1a5745d/662d3554b26c1b80-1e/s400x600/9a0788617aac61ea8058af41531ddc9a5d1eab86.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/0a913d03df90380cb52ea6ebe1a5745d/662d3554b26c1b80-1e/s500x750/1defa8d944cbc1eae771d3054448f8362c930583.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/0a913d03df90380cb52ea6ebe1a5745d/662d3554b26c1b80-1e/s540x810/4ef225102031fc37d21473d2ad0f142c5ed2045d.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/0a913d03df90380cb52ea6ebe1a5745d/662d3554b26c1b80-1e/s640x960/0f503a083fa67b9df5548349ab62704e74e44564.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/0a913d03df90380cb52ea6ebe1a5745d/662d3554b26c1b80-1e/s1280x1920/784e382a7d89835b3da830d0c11dad0afaba1534.jpg 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/0a913d03df90380cb52ea6ebe1a5745d/662d3554b26c1b80-1e/s2048x3072/daca5ff549189dc0324e4520ed31366d985a1fa1.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px"/&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;The city breathes, it gasps, it bends under the constant stress and the strain; the more it gets stretched thin, the more it makes people claw and bite at the rim. The march goes on, with a skip on Saturdays and a drag on Mondays— the boots resonate over chatter. &lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://blog.ayanchoudhury.in/post/668483991693885440</link><guid>https://blog.ayanchoudhury.in/post/668483991693885440</guid><pubDate>Sun, 21 Nov 2021 23:03:33 +0530</pubDate><category>illustration</category><category>painting</category><category>delhi</category><category>2021</category></item><item><title>Happy endings</title><description>&lt;p&gt;Fewer times have I ever before noticed emotions change as fast as the graph of a crypto token. The other day, I was at the saloon ( what a barbershop is called in India). As I waited for my turn for a haircut, I couldn&amp;rsquo;t help but notice the customer beside me — a middle-aged guy getting the full service package on offer. The barber was done with the shave and had now taken up the role of a masseuse with a massager clamped to the back of his hand. It vivaciously vibrated like a purring cat. As the vibrating fingers walked against the customer&amp;rsquo;s head and body, his resulting orgasmic expressions kept nudging me towards absurd but funny assumptions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="npf_row"&gt;&lt;figure class="tmblr-full" data-orig-height="1920" data-orig-width="1920"&gt;&lt;img src="https://64.media.tumblr.com/9862eca1b3dc13415ab90de1413512ba/bf1df8dd1267dcf8-5c/s640x960/f590c099ea55f55c2fc44b28bfd37e1414d72d54.jpg" data-orig-height="1920" data-orig-width="1920" srcset="https://64.media.tumblr.com/9862eca1b3dc13415ab90de1413512ba/bf1df8dd1267dcf8-5c/s75x75_c1/191a9ca4ba722f5aadfc4474ae5fbc70cfe5697e.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9862eca1b3dc13415ab90de1413512ba/bf1df8dd1267dcf8-5c/s100x200/62cedcb5174ee699726a38c90d8bc0c6c3ab09ba.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9862eca1b3dc13415ab90de1413512ba/bf1df8dd1267dcf8-5c/s250x400/1b47507c32e46b4aa5d51d490f0d9c177465280d.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9862eca1b3dc13415ab90de1413512ba/bf1df8dd1267dcf8-5c/s400x600/8c98d3775cdf021c047c1bddaa04b67869c136b7.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9862eca1b3dc13415ab90de1413512ba/bf1df8dd1267dcf8-5c/s500x750/89c5c36df73a41e0546133c23230a48a2644d188.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9862eca1b3dc13415ab90de1413512ba/bf1df8dd1267dcf8-5c/s540x810/5e1e13bc8ea56a29c94b8a25091b050afed06443.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9862eca1b3dc13415ab90de1413512ba/bf1df8dd1267dcf8-5c/s640x960/f590c099ea55f55c2fc44b28bfd37e1414d72d54.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9862eca1b3dc13415ab90de1413512ba/bf1df8dd1267dcf8-5c/s1280x1920/e549893546e262e87f313b8ef2aa05db5272d8c2.jpg 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9862eca1b3dc13415ab90de1413512ba/bf1df8dd1267dcf8-5c/s2048x3072/2244d74eeee611d0ed9c0b046518e5ddbbc2db1a.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px"/&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;It seemed like this was the first-time-in-a-long-time someone was touching him this way. His eyes almost shut in a dizzying trance when the barber put his vibrating finger inside the guy&amp;rsquo;s aural orifice. The poor barber was probably used to these reactions off the many such middle-aged men he has had to serve, but he had a neat trick up his sleeve. The massage session drew to a close and in the ultimate act, the barber took off the whirring massager, rubbed his palms, cracked his knuckles, and smacked the dozing post orgasmic customer hard on his back. In less than a second, the guy was getting smacked, shaken and shuffled around in the seat and it was pretty apparent why the barber was suddenly loving every second of his job. Ultimately, it&amp;rsquo;s safe to say the guy got the complete awakening experience. It&amp;rsquo;s safer to say, when it comes to me, I could pass on that experience for a few more years, or decades.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="npf_row"&gt;&lt;figure class="tmblr-full" data-orig-height="1920" data-orig-width="1920"&gt;&lt;img src="https://64.media.tumblr.com/ec2fb4ae3347196fd70fc3de166748d7/bf1df8dd1267dcf8-07/s640x960/011ff5e321f3cad